sentences.english: In theory, Whitehall officials and ministers back in London oversaw the empire.

sentences.english: Armies of consultants are employed as contractors across Whitehall for years.

sentences.english: Attending the VE Day ceremony in Whitehall yesterday he looked exhausted.

sentences.english: This was not in Whitehall, nor was it out in the forests.
